Description: Ticket Spinlock with proportional backoff, it's FIFO fair and it reduces the cache-coherence traffic.



- Platform:  Windows, Mac OSX(x86) and Linux(x86)

Required FPC switches: -O3 -Sd -dFPC -dFreePascal

-Sd for delphi mode.... 

{$DEFINE CPU32} and {$DEFINE Windows32} for 32 bit systems

{$DEFINE CPU64} and {$DEFINE Windows64} for 64 bit systems
 
